  "original_title": "\u0b95\u0b9f\u0bb5\u0bc1\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bc0\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc8\u0baa\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bc6\u0bb1 \u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b9a\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1 \u0baa\u0bc6\u0ba3\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb4\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bc8 \u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0b9a\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bcd!",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Woman waiting in queue to get passport gives birth!",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "A woman who was waiting in line to get a passport in front of the Immigration and Emigration Department in Bhattaramulla gave birth to a baby.",
        "After the woman went into labor while standing in the queue, she delivered the baby on the way to the Borlai-Kasalveedi Women's Hospital by the soldiers there.",
        "Those present said that the woman who gave birth to the child has been waiting at the place since yesterday to get the passport.",
        "According to hospital sources, a 26-year-old woman from Hatton area gave birth to the baby."
      ],
